name: Arcade
description: This is a LORA based on the idea of an arcade background. This makes brightly colored and patterned game cabinets for your arcade themed needs. This Lora does good results around 0.6. modelVersions.name: Arcade V8
modelVersions.description:
Compatibility update, for those of you who care why the version changed so much to try to make this LORA more compatible with others I took a tip from the comment section and tried training on a pruned file. I tried AOM2 pruned, NAI pruned, and even tried baking VAE's into them at different ratios to try to get desired results. Finally, I tried training on pastel pruned by andite. This LORA will allow mixing of other LORA without losing detail. Probably will go through and update all my other LORA soon but This improvement is already a win.
